title: Green Zebra Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Est. 2015 a health food cafe using local and organic ingredients. Menu is mostly vegan / vegetarian, with raw dishes and desserts, cold pressed juices, smoothies, wellness shots and elixirs. The interior of the building and the furniture are composed of reclaimed and recycled materials. A purification system filters the water used for drink and food preparation.
